&lt;p&gt;The fastest road and race bikes on the planet!
Join leading race bike tester Alan Cathcart with today's Grand Prix, World Superbike and Supersport racers from all the top factory teams - including the World Championship winning GP Suzuki of Kenny Roberts and the Honda V-Twin that took Colin Edwards to the World SBK title. Watch the bikes being tested at challenging circuits around the world, see close-up engine and chassis details with our exclusive footage, hear from top riders and team managers and experience first class action with the rider's-eye-view as on-bike cameras take you on an unforgettable ride! But that's not all! The lads from Performance Bikes magazine are searching for the ultimate sportsbike and you're invited to join in! See the various contenders put through their paces on road and track, dyno, datalogger and test strip. And team up with David Jefferies, Steve Hislop and Neil Hodgson as they thrash top road bikes around the legendary roads of the Isle of Man. &lt;p/&gt;




